    "They present their results on the UUParser, an existing parser for Norwegian.",
    "Roy et al. [2020] present an analysis using Stanford parser and Allen NLP parser on parsing of news headlines in Indian English.",
    "Scannell [2020] create a treebank for Manx Gaelic and compare the performance of existing classifiers with Irish Gaelic and Scottish Gaelic.",
